TQ0ODEtODQ2Ni1hMjJiMjhiODBlMzIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueGJveC5jb20vZW4tVVMvY29uc29sZXMveGJveC1zZXJpZXMtcyNwdXJjaGFzZSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzkxN2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAV5OM5pCKwQDXJhuRtWzBYhco99g99UINNDV1emoTydi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fen-US%2Fconsoles%2Fxbox-series-s%23purchase">Xbox Series S</a> is still a strong value for those who don&#39;t care about top-of-the-line hardware, but if you need a disc drive and more consistent performance, the Series X is your best bet.</p><h2> Shark RV1001AE </h2><p><core-commerce id="66eba5dd842147c4b174e4805f53bd86" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Shark makes some of <a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TaGFyay1SMTAwMUFFLVNlbGYtRW1wdHktQ29ubmVjdGVkLUNhcGFjaXR5L2RwL0IwN1M4NjRHUFc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVVsJHbpkTEqOcIriS8Bq-Iez1SUFllHcK1Mmk8OKNze&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FShark-R1001AE-Self-Empty-Connected-Capacity%2Fdp%2FB07S864GPW">our favorite robot vacuums</a> and right now the <a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TaGFyay1SMTAwMUFFLVNlbGYtRW1wdHktQ29ubmVjdGVkLUNhcGFjaXR5L2RwL0IwN1M4NjRHUFc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVVsJHbpkTEqOcIriS8Bq-Iez1SUFllHcK1Mmk8OKNze&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FShark-R1001AE-Self-Empty-Connected-Capacity%2Fdp%2FB07S864GPW">Shark RV1001AE</a> is half price, making it $300 instead of its $600 street price. This model has a bagless, self-emptying base, that you won&#39;t have to empty for quite some time as it has a claimed capacity of up to 45 days. While we didn&#39;t try this exact model, we&#39;ve found vacs from Shark to be easy to set up and appreciate Shark&#39;s easy-to-use companion app. Shark&#39;s mapping function is also accurate and the bagless base will save you money in the long run as buying device-specific bags can get pricey.</p><h2> Samsung Galaxy Watch 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="82b39bb57d2e41dab1c787229046a5f2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjVUQjNRP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE0YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzkxN2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWiQntQfuL-DpTNEDx9m5QPh_cN-L6WPbhTNq0SxIGRo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J5TB3Q">Samsung Galaxy Watch 5</a> is down to $199 for a 40mm model and $229 for a <a data-i13n="cpos:63;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3V